label: documentResponseDocumentTypeCode
comment: A code specifying a type of response document for this exchanged document, such as a requested or required response document type.

rangeIncludes.comment: A character string denoting the type of a document. [Reference United Nations Code List (UNCL) 1001]

domainIncludes.comment: A collection of data for a piece of written, printed or electronic matter that is exchanged between two or more parties.
